The paper discusses large-scale neural network architecture search using an accuracy predictor. This involves machine learning techniques such as genetic algorithms, reinforcement learning, and learning curve extrapolation, which are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the use of datasets and their characterization, which is relevant to the field of data science (cs.DS).
